dialog.body: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Henry Sanchez. May I have your name, please?
Hello Henry, my name is Nicole Wood.
Thank you, Nicole. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's one two three four five.
Great, thank you. And for security purposes, can you please confirm your date of birth?
My date of birth is January five, nineteen ninety-two.
Perfect, thank you for verifying, Nicole. How can I assist you today with our Old Stone Auto Insurance services?
I have a question about my policy coverage.
Of course, I'm here to help. What specific query do you have regarding your policy coverage, Nicole?
I'd like to know if rental car coverage is included in my policy.
I'll check that for you. Thank you for your time, Nicole. Is there anything else you would like assistance with?
